data.chText: 送信人；通信员；邮递员；信使
data.enText: a person who gives a message to sb or who delivers messages to people as a job

data.chText: 他通过邮递员发出订单。
data.enText: He sent the order by messenger.

data.chText: 拿报信人出气（而非责备问题的责任人）
data.enText: to blame the person who gives the news that sth bad has happened, instead of the person who is really responsible

data.chText: 拿报信人出气（而非责备问题的责任人）
data.enText: to blame the person who gives the news that sth bad has happened, instead of the person who is really responsible

tr: a person who carries a message

value.def: A messenger takes a message to someone, or takes messages regularly as their job.

example.ex: There will be a messenger at the Airport to collect the photographs from our courier...
example.tran: 机场会有一名信使从我们的递送员手中取走照片。

example.ex: He gave the instruction for the document to be sent by messenger.
example.tran: 他下令由通信员送出文件。
